  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The tenets of the Oath of Glory drive a paladin to attempt heroics that might one day shine in legend.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Actions over Words.</strong></em> Strive to be known by glorious deeds, not words.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Challenges Are but Tests.</strong></em> Face hardships with courage, and encourage your allies to face them with you.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Hone the Body.</strong></em> Like raw stone, your body must be worked so its potential can be realized.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Discipline the Soul.</strong></em> You must marshal the discipline to overcome failings within yourself that threaten to dim the glory of you and your friends.</p>",
